  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to evaluate the risk of Down syndrome during the first trimester of
      the pregnancy. The risk assessment is evaluated using early ultrasound and maternal
      biochemical markers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
